# The FastAPI backend is not deployed here yet. Vercel builds root api/*.py as
# serverless functions, and this one cannot build: api/requirements.txt omits
# langchain, langchain-openai, langchain-pinecone, pinecone and python-dotenv,
# and api/index.py raises at import when OPEN_API_KEY / PINECONE_API_KEY are
# unset. Nothing calls it now that the chatbot is removed. To deploy it, fix
# those deps, set the env vars in Vercel, then drop this entry.
api/
